{{!
    @template media_openveo/player

    OpenVeo Media Player template to display a media using the OpenVeo Player.

    Context variables required for this template:
    * url - The OpenVeo Publish media URL if iframe is set to true
    * width - The expected player width if iframe is set to true
    * height - The expected player height if iframe is set to true
    * iframe - true if there is no error and iframe can be displayed, false otherwise
    * error - true if there is an error and iframe can't be displayed, false otherwise
    * errormessage - The translated error mesasge if error is set to true

    Example context (json):
    {
        "url": "[...]/publish/video/SycMFW--X?fullscreen&lang=en&auto-play",
        "width": 768,
        "height": 500,
        "iframe": true
    }

    Example context with an error (json):
    {
        "error": true,
        "errormessage": "Something went wrong"
    }
}}
<div class="media-openveo-player">
    {{#iframe}}
        <iframe width="{{width}}" height="{{height}}" src="{{url}}" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe>
    {{/iframe}}
    {{#error}}
        <p>{{errormessage}}</p>
    {{/error}}
</div>
